Credits for Modbus RTU over TCP/IP API
Vladislav Kochedykov
https://github.com/kochedykov/jlibmodbus

Things You need to set in Devices and Serial to Ethernet Converters
1) Set DataBits : 8
2) Set Parity :   NONE
3) Set Stopbits:  1
4) setBaudRate:   9600

How to Run the App:
1) Enter IP Address and Port Number and Press Set
2) Enter Slave ID: ID for the device, Hex code : of register from which the reading should start to poll  
   and Quanity: to upto where the register should read.
3)Press Read Input Registers to read Input Registers / Press Read Holding Registers to read holding Register
